duaList.translation: May you wear it out and Allah تعالى replace it (with another). The intended meaning: A supplication for long life.

duaList.arabic: اِلبَـس جَديـداً وَعِـشْ حَمـيداً وَمُـتْ شهيداً
duaList.transliteration: Ilbas jadeedan waAAish hameedan wamut shaheedan.
duaList.translation: Wear anew, live commendably and die a shaheed.

pageProps.duaName: Supplication said to someone wearing a new garment
